ed="T" n="0850a01"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0850a01"/><head><date from-iso="+0923-05-18" key="j20583162063308" to-iso="+0937-01-16">後唐</date>天台山<persName key="A012842">全宰</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0850a02"/><persName key="A012842">釋全宰</persName>，姓沈氏，<placeName key="PL000000011520">錢塘</placeName>人也。孩抱之間，不喜<lb
ed="T" n="0850a03"/>葷血，其母累覩善徵，勸投<placeName key="PL000000011848">徑山</placeName><persName key="A010583">法濟大師</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0850a04"/>削染。及修禪觀，亭亭高竦，不雜風塵，慕十<lb
ed="T" n="0850a05"/>二頭陀以飾其行，諺曰<persName key="A012842">宰道者</persName>焉。迨乎諸<lb
ed="T" n="0850a06"/>方參請，得<persName key="A010581">石霜禪師</persName>印證，密加保任，入天<lb
ed="T" n="0850a07"/>台山<placeName key="PL000000014558">闇巖</placeName>以永其志也。伊<placeName key="PL000000014558">巖</placeName>與<persName key="A004127">寒山子</persName>所<lb
ed="T" n="0850a08"/>隱對峙，皆魑魅木怪所叢萃其間。<persName key="A012842">宰</persName>之居<lb
ed="T" n="0850a09"/>也二十餘年，惡鳥革音，山精讓窟。其出入經<lb
ed="T" n="0850a10"/>行，鬼神執役，或掃其路，或侍其旁，或代汲<lb
ed="T" n="0850a11"/>泉，或供<anchor xml:id="beg0850001"/>採菓<anchor xml:id="end0850001"/>，時時人見，<persName key="A012842">宰</persName>未甞言。後<date from-iso="+0930-02-07" key="j20607732060821" to-iso="+0930-03-27"><name>天成</name><lb
ed="T" n="0850a12"/>五年</date>，<placeName key="PL000000011848">徑山</placeName>禪侶往迎歸<placeName key="PL000000010074">鎮國院</placeName>居，終于出家<lb
ed="T" n="0850a13"/>本院焉。</p>
